snippet.title: What I Wish I Knew About Image Literals.... Filtering!
snippet.description:
Finding the correct image assets in a large project becomes increasingly difficult as your project grows.  One secret approach that can help you filter down on your assets is to use the media selector with CMD + SHIFT + M.  I'll go over how to do this in today's lesson.
